## How It Works [[sort]]

### Data Directory

Qovery requires a `data_dir` value for on-disk operations. Currently, the only
operation using this directory are Qovery's on-disk buffers. Buffers, by
default, are memory-based, but if you switch them to disk-based you'll need to
specify a `data_dir`.
